datasources.datasource: select ELCDSCST from ttcs,ric_ord where elccdsoc=substr(ordprog,1,2) and elccdmag=substr(ordprog,3,7) and elccdcst=rocdmov and ordprog='$P{ordprog}';
select substr(racdpro,4,9) as racdrid,prdsaut,prdstit,raqtord,prpzcoe as prezzo from ric_art, catalogo where racdpro=prcdpro and ordprog='$P{ordprog}';
select elcdsvet,elcinvet,elclovet,elccpvet,elcprvet from ttve,ric_ord where elccdvet=rocdve1 and ordprog='$P{ordprog}';
select elcdsvet,elcinvet,elclovet,elccpvet,elcprvet from ttve,ric_ord where elccdvet=rocdve2 and ordprog='$P{ordprog}';

select ric_ord.ORDPROG, ROCDRID, ROCDSPC, ROCDARE, ROCDVEN, RODSCLI, ROCOCLI, ROINCLI, ROLOCLI, ROPRCLI, ROCPCLI, RONZCLI, ROCDCLA, ROCDSPA, RODSCLA, ROINCLA, ROCOCLA, ROLOCLA, ROPRCLA, ROCPCLA, RONZCLA, ROSWSPF, RONMBAM, RODTBAM, ROTPTAR, ROSWCOL, ROVLCON, ROTPSPE, ROCDLIN, ROCDSCA, ROCDSSC, ROCDSOT, ROCDMOV, ROTPDOC, RODTEVA, ROSWFIN, ROCDFPG, ROTPBUT, ROORINS, ROCDVAL, ROVLCOE, RONMCED, ROCDVE1, ROCDVE2, ROCDVE3, ROIDVET, RONMRGH, RONMRGP, RONMCPE, RONMCPP, RONMCLL, RONMCLA, ROCDBTC, ROTMRCZ, ROTMINI, ROTMEVA, ROAAXAB, ROPRXAB, RODTXAB, RONMDIS, RODTDIS, ROPRGLN, ROCDFLG, ROSTATO, ORDTIPO, RODSTSP, frattomille(ROPSPRE) as ropspre, frattomille(ROVLCOE) as rocontr, frattomille(ROPSREA) as ropsrea, (sum(prpzcoe::numeric(10,2)*raqtord)) as roprezzo, substr(ric_ord.ordprog,1,2) as rocdmag, substr(ric_ord.ordprog,3,7) as rocdsoc, substr(ric_ord.ordprog,10,2) as roaadoc, substr(ric_ord.ordprog,12,6) as roprdoc, substr(rodtbam,7,2)||'/'||substr(rodtbam,5,2)||'/'||substr(rodtbam,3,2) as rodtbamc, substr(rodtbam,7,2)||'/'||substr(rodtbam,5,2)||'/'||substr(rodtbam,1,4) as rodtbaml, substr(rodtxab,7,2)||'/'||substr(rodtxab,5,2)||'/'||substr(rodtxab,3,2) as rodtxabc, substr(rodtxab,7,2)||'/'||substr(rodtxab,5,2)||'/'||substr(rodtxab,1,4) as rodtxabl, case when roswcol='1' then 'COLLI' when roswcol='4' then 'BANCALI' end as aspetto from ric_ord,ric_art,catalogo where ric_art.ordprog=ric_ord.ordprog and catalogo.prcdpro=ric_art.racdpro and ric_ord.ordprog='$P{ordprog}' group by ric_ord.ORDPROG, ROCDRID, ROCDSPC, ROCDARE, ROCDVEN, RODSCLI, ROCOCLI, ROINCLI, ROLOCLI, ROPRCLI, ROCPCLI, RONZCLI, ROCDCLA, ROCDSPA, RODSCLA, ROINCLA, ROCOCLA, ROLOCLA, ROPRCLA, ROCPCLA, RONZCLA, ROSWSPF, RONMBAM, RODTBAM, ROTPTAR, ROSWCOL, ROVLCON, ROTPSPE, ROCDLIN, ROCDSCA, ROCDSSC, ROCDSOT, ROCDMOV, ROTPDOC, RODTEVA, ROSWFIN, ROCDFPG, ROTPBUT, ROORINS, ROCDVAL, ROVLCOE, RONMCED, ROCDVE1, ROCDVE2, ROCDVE3, ROIDVET, RONMRGH, RONMRGP, RONMCPE, RONMCPP, RONMCLL, RONMCLA, ROCDBTC, ROTMRCZ, ROTMINI, ROTMEVA, ROAAXAB, ROPRXAB, RODTXAB, RONMDIS, RODTDIS, ROPRGLN, ROCDFLG,ROSTATO, ORDTIPO, ropspre, ropsrea,rodstsp;
